&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for paediatric staff nurses to work within our friendly paediatric Emergency care and paediatric ward team. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The post holder will have the opportunity to rotate between these two areas gaining transferable skills with the opportunity to gain airway management experience within the recovery unit.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; The time spent within the areas will be modified to the individual’s choice as well as service need.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The post holder will be offered training and supervision within the areas as well as external course training to ensure skills are developed and maintained. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information regarding the post please contact Lisa King (Paediatric Inpatient Matron)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;01493 452184&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;lisa.king@jpaget.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
